1. brew install gnupg
2. curl -sSL https://rvm.io/mpapis.asc | gpg --import -
3. curl -sSL https://rvm.io/pkuczynski.asc | gpg --import -
4. \curl -sSL https://get.rvm.io | bash -s stable --ruby
5. For full documentation, please visit http://jekyllrb.com/docs/home/
6. If you have any other questions, please contact honryou@gmail.com for support.